&lt;hr>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3058700d-9186-458c-b643-7d0215aa7a84" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>헤드폰 샀다&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3e37ea2b-57b2-41f6-9115-ceee68b06505" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>스카에서 공부하는건 행복한데 이날은 좀 불행했다 근데 주말내내 불행을 원동력으로 월요일에 이악물고 대처한듯&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/12d1410a-c5ef-43ea-bf29-ede67ea01084" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>그리고 지쳐있던 수요일,, 단비같은 코로나 양성 판정 ㅋ&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2caaec5f-6cb2-49ec-9757-fb3041af15d7" alt="image" />
&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a3126842-7572-4c6f-bc76-1ff6227c4807" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>첫날은 영화보고 헤드폰쓰고 산책도 나감&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dcd3dd5e-f368-4598-a924-f15fc0d9498f" alt="image" />
&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5aa5eb39-2e8b-4ffd-8119-b148bc50fd4e" alt="image" />
&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d41abd3-4d40-48e6-a101-4c0de1dbf8ae" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>웡카 개봉하면 바로보러가야지 살아남을이유가 생겼어&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/21840eae-fae5-493c-b9de-56fc31501006" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>월요일엔 엘리멘탈 볼려고 예매해뒀다 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p>
&lt;p>행복을 잃지마&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>